ily and faced with a restructuring at work, her husband, SUEN KA-ON (Cheung Siu Fai), finds himself on the verge of a mid-life crisis. PO’s younger sister, KAN YIK-TAN (Joyce Tang), is a devil-may-care woman. The fact that she has recently broken up with her boyfriend does not discourage her from starting another relationship. Quite the contrary, she marries Malaysian Chinese NG LOK-YAN (Hanjin Tan), a guy she merely knows about, and takes him back to Hong Kong. Come and see how intriguing and fun living in a household with culture shock under the same roof can be!</p>","tmdb_id":41967,"cast":["Trương Triệu Huy","Thương Thiên Nga","Đằng Lệ Danh","Tan Hanjin","Thang Doanh Doanh","Lâm Hạ Vy","Viên Vỹ Hào","Susan Tse Suet-Sum","Bowie Wu","Rachel Poon Siu-Tung","Suet Nei","Charmaine Li","Wong Ching","Lý Gia Thanh","Eddie Li Yu-Yeung"],"director":[],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"41967","season":1,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Trương Triệu Huy","name_vi":"Trương Triệu Huy","name_original":"Eddie Cheung Siu-Fai","tmdb_id":72732,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/jTrBt3y43LsO8XYsQnWg8bdwsP2.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/72732"},{"name":"Thương Thiên Nga","name_vi":"Thương Thiên Nga","name_original":"Kiki Sheung","tmdb_id":1588963,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/pr43xrvugDA6fjlsjfeyqKUEUjg.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1588963"},{"name":"Đằng Lệ Danh","name_vi":"Đằng Lệ Danh","name_original":"Joyce Tang Lai-Ming","tmdb_id":1223072,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/rCGjxrs3HeRoOhzqbAwCucV12qo.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1223072"},{"name":"Tan Hanjin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Tan Hanjin","tmdb_id":1191740,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/cQgpsH95cdxHWLWGFtIWmclVzqo.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/1191740"},{"name":"Thang Doanh Doanh","name_vi":"Thang Doanh Doanh","name_original":"Angela Tong Ying-Ying","tmdb_id":125